1
00:00:04,890 --> 00:00:06,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry it up, Koichi! Come on!</font>

2
00:00:07,580 --> 00:00:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah. If I go too fast without 
any gear, it's dangerous.</font>

3
00:00:10,730 --> 00:00:13,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, it's cold today, huh?</font>

4
00:00:14,180 --> 00:00:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, get a move on!</font>

5
00:00:16,320 --> 00:00:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look lively!</font>

6
00:00:18,300 --> 00:00:20,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makoto and the Captain!</font>

7
00:00:20,500 --> 00:00:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're gonna start the 
meeting without you!</font>

8
00:00:24,840 --> 00:00:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, I was late getting out of school.</font>

9
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I didn't get out of work on time.</font>

10
00:00:29,790 --> 00:00:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

11
00:00:31,430 --> 00:00:33,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you want a lift?</font>

12
00:00:34,410 --> 00:00:35,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we?!</font>

13
00:00:35,570 --> 00:00:38,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, since you were 
nice enough to offer...</font>

14
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, flying really is faster!</font>

15
00:00:44,620 --> 00:00:47,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... colder!</font>

16
00:00:47,360 --> 00:00:50,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Freezing, actually!</font>

17
00:02:21,370 --> 00:02:28,330
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an1}<font size="40"><font color="#c5000e">Catastrophe</font></font></b></font>

18
00:02:23,330 --> 00:02:28,370
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an7}Great upheaval in society or the natural world.
 Major change.
 Can also refer to a tragic outcome in stories.
Often accompanied by destruction.</b></font>

19
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:29,330
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b><i>{\an1}<font size="30"><font color="#ffe640">Farewell Party!</font></font></i></b></font>

20
00:02:32,780 --> 00:02:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain!</font>

21
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:45,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, I'm still cold! Are you two okay?</font>

22
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:48,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're fine.</font>

23
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:52,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I honestly don't see how you're not 
cold without wearing a coat, Captain!</font>

24
00:02:53,450 --> 00:02:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not a problem, with the help of my Quirk!</font>

25
00:02:58,820 --> 00:03:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The aerodynamic field that covers me
doesn't just propel me while I'm flying,</font>

26
00:03:00,780 --> 00:03:05,660
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b>{\an1}<i><font color="#172922"><font size="36">Aerodynamic Field</font></font></i></b></font>

27
00:03:06,020 --> 00:03:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but also shuts down heat, cold, 
and impacts from the outside!</font>

28
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I just need to expand it, 
and it protects my body!</font>

29
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you only use it on girls?</font>

30
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make it sound like that!</font>

31
00:03:18,390 --> 00:03:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say there was a single blanket right here.</font>

32
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:25,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you want to share 
it with another guy?</font>

33
00:03:25,220 --> 00:03:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd take that over freezing! You 
really are a piece of work.</font>

34
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure you keep all of 
that off the record, Koichi.</font>

35
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see how it'd be bad 
for his image, yeah.</font>

36
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that stuff.</font>

37
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean the specifics about his 
Quirk and its weaknesses.</font>

38
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:41,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Better to keep that sort of thing secret.</font>

39
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I get you.</font>

40
00:03:43,870 --> 00:03:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kind of precaution a famous 
hero would need to take.</font>

41
00:03:47,450 --> 00:03:49,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning!</font>

42
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry about the delay!</font>

43
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:54,080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#3d3c37"><font size="18">Meeting Room B</font></font></b></font>

44
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:58,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that'll cover our 
review of the last event.</font>

45
00:03:58,510 --> 00:04:02,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which also completes our 
Narufest run for the year!</font>

46
00:04:02,650 --> 00:04:04,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You all did great.</font>

47
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:08,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And from this point on...</font>

48
00:04:08,020 --> 00:04:09,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's our Christmas party!</font>

49
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave this to us!</font>

50
00:04:22,470 --> 00:04:24,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fold, fold, fold...</font>

51
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pizza's here!</font>

52
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sup!</font>

53
00:04:30,410 --> 00:04:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can take that.</font>

54
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay. I've got it.</font>

55
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It all looks so good!</font>

56
00:04:38,170 --> 00:04:40,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello, everyone! Good to see you!</font>

57
00:04:40,970 --> 00:04:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">President!</font>

58
00:04:49,140 --> 00:04:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, here we go...</font>

59
00:04:52,310 --> 00:04:54,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready and...</font>

60
00:04:55,050 --> 00:04:58,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Merry Christmas!</font>

61
00:05:02,020 --> 00:05:03,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Red nose, red nose!{unmarked adlib}</font>

62
00:05:04,150 --> 00:05:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Line up, everyone. Come get yours!</font>

63
00:05:08,100 --> 00:05:09,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gift certificates!</font>

64
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the color of my passion.</font>

65
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:17,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so dreamy.</font>

66
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Captain's asleep.</font>

67
00:05:28,180 --> 00:05:30,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's been pretty busy lately, 
from what I can tell.</font>

68
00:05:30,930 --> 00:05:34,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I seem to remember you falling 
asleep during the meeting.</font>

69
00:05:37,060 --> 00:05:39,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is the party already over?</font>

70
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time for the next gig?</font>

71
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's still time. Make 
sure to rest while you can.</font>

72
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:49,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your schedule through New Year's 
Eve is full, after all.</font>

73
00:05:49,700 --> 00:05:53,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, sure, work me like 
a horse if you must.</font>

74
00:05:53,530 --> 00:05:56,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This year, the next, and beyond.</font>

75
00:05:56,380 --> 00:05:58,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's just life.</font>

76
00:05:58,610 --> 00:06:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, you'll be getting ready 
to go home early next year,</font>

77
00:06:01,790 --> 00:06:05,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so while you'll still be busy until 
then, things should slow down after that.</font>

78
00:06:06,100 --> 00:06:10,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go home? But I thought those 
lawsuits were all still...</font>

79
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your excursion's just about over, boss.</font>

80
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the cases that were still in dispute</font>

81
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">should be wrapped up by 
the end of the year.</font>

82
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:22,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which also means the suspensions affecting
you throughout the States will be lifted.</font>

83
00:06:22,310 --> 00:06:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The negotiations with the various people</font>

84
00:06:24,700 --> 00:06:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who asked for restraining orders 
on you are proceeding, as well.</font>

85
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no idea.</font>

86
00:06:28,780 --> 00:06:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A big part of it is that a lot of 
the cases that were against you</font>

87
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">ended up being fraudulent.</font>

88
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were?!</font>

89
00:06:35,460 --> 00:06:39,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A whole cocktail tray of honey 
traps and paparazzi collusion.</font>

90
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You made an easy mark for them.</font>

91
00:06:42,170 --> 00:06:47,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which did leave us with our 
own options, thankfully.</font>

92
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Makoto, I hope we're 
always good friends.</font>

93
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:55,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I sure wouldn't 
want you as a foe.</font>

94
00:06:55,810 --> 00:06:58,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That means you get to go home, Captain!</font>

95
00:06:58,930 --> 00:07:00,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's great!</font>

96
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:05,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, even if I go back to America, 
I won't get to go home, per se.</font>

97
00:07:05,670 --> 00:07:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Considering how my wife feels about me...</font>

98
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's scheduled to give birth next month,</font>

99
00:07:12,940 --> 00:07:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so the two of you can have a nice talk 
about the future once you're with her.</font>

100
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:19,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give birth? Pamela?</font>

101
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To my baby?</font>

102
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I didn't know about this?!</font>

103
00:07:23,580 --> 00:07:26,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She told me something when I met her.</font>

104
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:32,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I know my husband is a good man, 
but he's a little too trusting."</font>

105
00:07:32,970 --> 00:07:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I don't want to risk raising a 
child in the middle of this mess."</font>

106
00:07:35,930 --> 00:07:39,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I intend to bring up 
the baby on my own."</font>

107
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:43,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Pamela said all that?</font>

108
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if you want a direct quote, 
it was more like "That idiot—"</font>

109
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:50,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Never mind! I believe you! 
The summary will do.</font>

110
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:53,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think the whole thing 
would hurt my feelings.</font>

111
00:07:53,550 --> 00:07:57,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was it that made her 
change her mind, then?</font>

112
00:07:58,150 --> 00:08:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When she told me about the 
baby, I told her something.</font>

113
00:08:02,470 --> 00:08:04,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?</font>

114
00:08:05,620 --> 00:08:07,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To leave it to me!</font>

115
00:08:10,250 --> 00:08:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, then you'll be all good, Captain!</font>

116
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations!</font>

117
00:08:14,530 --> 00:08:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna see the baby!</font>

118
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:16,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me too!</font>

119
00:08:19,100 --> 00:08:23,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see... I'll really get to 
go back to the States...</font>

120
00:08:24,820 --> 00:08:26,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To my home.</font>

121
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And to meet my baby...</font>

122
00:08:28,610 --> 00:08:31,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't ask for a better 
Christmas present!</font>

123
00:08:35,390 --> 00:08:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hang on! Wait, wait! I 
didn't mean it like that!</font>

124
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys get that, right?!</font>

125
00:08:41,450 --> 00:08:45,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He does tend to set himself up for 
problems like this, doesn't he?</font>

126
00:08:45,210 --> 00:08:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I think I see it.</font>

127
00:08:48,690 --> 00:08:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's kind of late, so everyone 
be careful on the way home.</font>

128
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:52,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

129
00:08:52,880 --> 00:09:00,100
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#a28773"><font size="30">Marukane</font></font></b></font>

130
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you all next time!</font>

131
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You kids are going back in a taxi, okay?</font>

132
00:08:58,830 --> 00:09:00,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

133
00:09:00,330 --> 00:09:04,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you bring the change and the 
receipt to our next meeting?</font>

134
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

135
00:09:05,690 --> 00:09:07,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We had a lot of fun!</font>

136
00:09:07,370 --> 00:09:08,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

137
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:10,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And there'll be more, next year!</font>

138
00:09:10,510 --> 00:09:11,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

139
00:09:11,930 --> 00:09:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Driver, they're in your hands now.</font>

140
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:16,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye bye!</font>

141
00:09:16,820 --> 00:09:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Children can be so adorable.</font>

142
00:09:19,970 --> 00:09:23,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm picturing having three, back at home.</font>

143
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:25,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think, Makoto?</font>

144
00:09:25,370 --> 00:09:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you should discuss 
it with your wife.</font>

145
00:09:28,460 --> 00:09:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I think if anyone overheard you now, 
they could make problematic assumptions.</font>

146
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that'd be bad!</font>

147
00:09:35,760 --> 00:09:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

148
00:09:38,660 --> 00:09:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something huge just flew by!</font>

149
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A villain?!</font>

150
00:09:48,740 --> 00:09:50,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no! The girls' taxi!</font>

151
00:09:50,430 --> 00:09:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is bad! If it falls 
from that height...</font>

152
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right!</font>

153
00:10:01,260 --> 00:10:03,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can take down the villain</font>

154
00:10:03,900 --> 00:10:06,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and save the kids in one go!</font>

155
00:10:06,340 --> 00:10:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain!</font>

156
00:10:10,410 --> 00:10:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, I made it—</font>

157
00:10:12,420 --> 00:10:15,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Turns out, you didn't.</font>

158
00:10:21,140 --> 00:10:22,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It blew up?!</font>

159
00:10:25,970 --> 00:10:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is the boss...?</font>

160
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain!</font>

161
00:10:37,990 --> 00:10:41,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all okay?! You're 
not hurt, are you?!</font>

162
00:10:42,030 --> 00:10:44,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain!</font>

163
00:10:45,050 --> 00:10:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You okay, Captain?!</font>

164
00:10:47,130 --> 00:10:48,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, man, you're bleeding!</font>

165
00:10:49,330 --> 00:10:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that explosion?!</font>

166
00:10:51,090 --> 00:10:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that Captain Celebrity?</font>

167
00:10:52,850 --> 00:10:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C.C.'s all torn up!</font>

168
00:10:55,670 --> 00:10:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me! I work for 
him! Let me through!</font>

169
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:05,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it! No photos! Don't 
post me looking bad!</font>

170
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:09,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking bad?</font>

171
00:11:10,980 --> 00:11:14,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've never looked 
more impressive, boss!</font>

172
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:29,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like using flight and explosions 
together can be pretty effective.</font>

173
00:11:29,450 --> 00:11:33,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough to put a dent in 
Captain Celebrity...</font>

174
00:11:33,770 --> 00:11:35,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or is it?</font>

175
00:11:37,210 --> 00:11:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looked like he took some kind of 
barrier and put it around those kids</font>

176
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">right before the blast.</font>

177
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:46,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which means he took the brunt of the hit.</font>

178
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the only reason he seemed invincible 
before was because of said barrier.</font>

179
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:55,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's not actually immortal.</font>

180
00:11:55,610 --> 00:11:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that gives me plenty to play with.</font>

181
00:12:00,350 --> 00:12:05,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hell, another two or three hits 
with the same kind of blast...</font>

182
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:09,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I oughta be able to take 
him down easy, y'know?</font>

183
00:12:10,380 --> 00:12:13,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happy New Year.</font>

184
00:12:11,470 --> 00:12:16,920
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b><font size="25"><font color="#0b0b03">Might Tower</font></font></b></font>

185
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we might've been buried in work 
all through the New Year's holiday...</font>

186
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But here's to working 
together again this year.</font>

187
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:21,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, likewise.</font>

188
00:12:21,690 --> 00:12:26,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I hate to spring this on you, but I 
won't be able to drop by for a while.</font>

189
00:12:26,710 --> 00:12:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, really?</font>

190
00:12:29,010 --> 00:12:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm sure you've got more 
to do than keep me company.</font>

191
00:12:34,810 --> 00:12:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not that. Something urgent came up.</font>

192
00:12:37,830 --> 00:12:41,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An outside tip came through 
for a pre-existing matter,</font>

193
00:12:41,530 --> 00:12:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the investigation has 
progressed somewhat as a result.</font>

194
00:12:45,430 --> 00:12:49,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This case... is it the one with the 
drug, where you ended up being shot?</font>

195
00:12:49,970 --> 00:12:51,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's worrying!</font>

196
00:12:52,420 --> 00:12:56,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put in a call for me when you do 
something dangerous, all right?</font>

197
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can even make it private, 
and I'll come incognito!</font>

198
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:01,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am here...</font>

199
00:13:01,370 --> 00:13:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incognito!</font>

200
00:13:03,540 --> 00:13:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate the sentiment, at least.</font>

201
00:13:07,090 --> 00:13:12,560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="20"><b>{\an7}<font size="15"><font color="#052116">Recycle Shop
<font color="#021a18"><font size="20">Hoppers</font></font></font></font></b></font>

202
00:13:07,690 --> 00:13:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so that covers the individual 
clients from the list,</font>

203
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:16,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who we've been investigating to 
find a trail back to the source...</font>

204
00:13:16,390 --> 00:13:19,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we're still lacking 
something definitive.</font>

205
00:13:20,460 --> 00:13:25,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention, there's a chance 
that while looking into this,</font>

206
00:13:25,370 --> 00:13:27,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Factory might catch on 
and go into hiding again.</font>

207
00:13:28,340 --> 00:13:30,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These guys are definitely 
light on their feet.</font>

208
00:13:30,900 --> 00:13:35,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some more info to narrow down 
the search would be handy.</font>

209
00:13:35,660 --> 00:13:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you think, Eraser?</font>

210
00:13:37,430 --> 00:13:39,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, Tsukauchi.</font>

211
00:13:40,150 --> 00:13:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a record of the Naruhata 
Vigilantes' activities.</font>

212
00:13:44,430 --> 00:13:46,890
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b>{\an8}<i><font color="#090609">One week ago</font></i></b></font>

213
00:13:51,270 --> 00:13:52,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, wow.</font>

214
00:13:53,310 --> 00:13:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two have been really working hard!</font>

215
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right! Well, not me, but...</font>

216
00:13:58,400 --> 00:14:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that's the Crawler...</font>

217
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:03,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's amazing.</font>

218
00:14:03,830 --> 00:14:06,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either play dumb or act proud...</font>

219
00:14:06,310 --> 00:14:08,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But pick a lane, kid.</font>

220
00:14:10,690 --> 00:14:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all good, though.</font>

221
00:14:12,800 --> 00:14:17,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most of this falls under crime 
prevention and civilian arrest laws.</font>

222
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There seem to have been more 
injuries early on, but...</font>

223
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:23,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some unrelated old guy was 
responsible for those.</font>

224
00:14:23,560 --> 00:14:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'll note those as separate from 
everything from summer and beyond.</font>

225
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'll be holding on to 
these records you provided.</font>

226
00:14:31,180 --> 00:14:32,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate your cooperation.</font>

227
00:14:33,130 --> 00:14:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a good chance that 
the Naruhata villain attacks</font>

228
00:14:36,430 --> 00:14:39,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">were arranged by a major crime syndicate.</font>

229
00:14:40,060 --> 00:14:44,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This might even be a step 
towards solving the case!</font>

230
00:14:44,830 --> 00:14:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to thank you, too.</font>

231
00:14:47,250 --> 00:14:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Having pictures like those out there had 
me worried I'd get arrested some day.</font>

232
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:53,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when we talked to Makoto about it,</font>

233
00:14:53,940 --> 00:14:57,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she said we'd be better off asking 
a hero we know than the police.</font>

234
00:14:57,660 --> 00:15:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's true that heroes are more considerate 
about individual circumstance,</font>

235
00:15:01,420 --> 00:15:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while still having the same 
kind of access.</font>

236
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:09,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll treat you two as anonymous 
tipsters, so don't worry.</font>

237
00:15:09,340 --> 00:15:11,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Manager, I wanna thank y...</font>

238
00:15:11,660 --> 00:15:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or rather, give my regards 
to our mysterious vigilante.</font>

239
00:15:16,870 --> 00:15:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it was the...</font>

240
00:15:19,300 --> 00:15:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crawler.</font>

241
00:15:20,900 --> 00:15:23,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His name is the Crawler!</font>

242
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:28,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a farce.</font>

243
00:15:28,310 --> 00:15:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, man, play along.</font>

244
00:15:30,330 --> 00:15:33,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like a digital notebook 
composed of photos and text</font>

245
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:37,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">containing information about 
incidents involving Naruhata villains...</font>

246
00:15:37,870 --> 00:15:40,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There seems to be stuff here</font>

247
00:15:40,260 --> 00:15:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">on unreported incidents and events from 
before the police arrived on scene.</font>

248
00:15:44,340 --> 00:15:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where'd it come from?</font>

249
00:15:46,050 --> 00:15:47,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not sure.</font>

250
00:15:47,190 --> 00:15:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Midnight just asked me to pass it 
along, so I don't really know.</font>

251
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Couldn't tell you anything about 
the vigilantes' identities, either.</font>

252
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:03,190
<font size="20"><b>{\an7}<font size="8"><font color="#ebdbd9">MOMENT OF EXPLOSION
<font color="#403e40"><font size="9">RESCUE FROM THE SKY</font></font></font></font></b></font>

253
00:15:58,730 --> 00:16:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all okay?! You're 
not hurt, are you?!</font>

254
00:16:03,190 --> 00:16:08,410
<font size="20"><b>{\an1}<font size="11"><font color="#dce9f3">BREAKING NEWS: <font color="#2d333b">CAPTAIN CELEBRITY WRAPS UP DOMESTIC OPERATIONS, <font color="#27629f">PREPARES TO HEAD HOME THIS YEAR</font></font></font></font></b></font>

255
00:16:03,510 --> 00:16:06,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The American hero, Captain Celebrity,</font>

256
00:16:06,460 --> 00:16:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}who was the talk of the town after the 
explosion at the end of the year,</font>

257
00:16:11,650 --> 00:16:17,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}intends on concluding his excursion in 
Japan this year and returning to his homeland.</font>

258
00:16:17,410 --> 00:16:26,880
<font size="20"><b>{\an1}<font size="8">BREAKING NEWS: <font color="#4d5555">CAPTAIN CELEBRITY WRAPS UP DOMESTIC OPERATIONS, <font color="#27629f">PREPARES TO HEAD HOME THIS YEAR</font></font></font></b></font>

259
00:16:17,410 --> 00:16:22,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I hate to spring this on you all, but 
it was always part of the schedule.</font>

260
00:16:22,610 --> 00:16:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}As much as I hate to leave you, my family
is waiting for me back in the States.</font>

261
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain Celebrity will remain in Japan
for the rest of the New Year's holiday.</font>

262
00:16:31,010 --> 00:16:35,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's believed that his time in Japan will
lead to a rise to even greater heights.</font>

263
00:16:36,460 --> 00:16:40,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! The video's gone 
past 100 million hits!</font>

264
00:16:40,910 --> 00:16:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's even more than 
the giant monster fight!</font>

265
00:16:42,810 --> 00:16:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say your approval rating is
skyrocketing, and nearing All Might's!</font>

266
00:16:46,190 --> 00:16:50,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're one of the most-talked 
about tags on the internet, too!</font>

267
00:16:50,190 --> 00:16:55,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">#Celebrity, #Captain, #CCHomcoming, 
#AerialExplosion, #LameHoodie...</font>

268
00:16:55,280 --> 00:16:57,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a lot of buzz about people 
wanting an official Captain hoodie</font>

269
00:16:57,900 --> 00:17:00,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there being none on sale.</font>

270
00:17:00,050 --> 00:17:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His existing merch is all sold out, too...</font>

271
00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We couldn't get more stock in time.</font>

272
00:17:04,540 --> 00:17:09,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, it's a shame that there's no 
way to take advantage of the buzz.</font>

273
00:17:09,720 --> 00:17:12,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why... we'll create 
another round of buzz.</font>

274
00:17:15,090 --> 00:17:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The venue for the boss's farewell 
party at the end of March...</font>

275
00:17:19,320 --> 00:17:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is not going to be the Naruhata 
Public Hall like I said previously,</font>

276
00:17:22,340 --> 00:17:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but will instead be the 500-meter-tall, 
50,000-person-capacity Tokyo Sky Egg!</font>

277
00:17:27,600 --> 00:17:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The theme of the event will be 
Japan/US hero collaboration,</font>

278
00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we're gonna make it a big event!</font>

279
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This sounds kinda sudden!</font>

280
00:17:34,450 --> 00:17:37,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey Makoto, are you sure about this?</font>

281
00:17:38,580 --> 00:17:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kinda forced our way in! No way 
am I letting this chance get away!</font>

282
00:17:45,180 --> 00:17:47,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be your last gig in Japan.</font>

283
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:51,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's make sure you go 
out with a bang, boss!</font>

284
00:17:51,210 --> 00:17:54,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like there's no getting 
out of this, Captain.</font>

285
00:17:54,200 --> 00:17:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if you're doing it,</font>

286
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:58,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">let's make sure you can say your 
time in Japan was a huge success!</font>

287
00:18:00,170 --> 00:18:03,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And of course, the Narufest team 
will be offering our full support!</font>

288
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our support?! As in, performing 
on stage, at the Sky Egg?!</font>

289
00:18:08,860 --> 00:18:10,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Us?</font>

290
00:18:10,950 --> 00:18:14,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We usually only have around 100 
guests at Narufest, right?</font>

291
00:18:14,010 --> 00:18:17,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And half of them are friends and 
acquaintances, like Samazu...</font>

292
00:18:17,580 --> 00:18:19,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, more like fifty?</font>

293
00:18:19,740 --> 00:18:22,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the Sky Egg is...</font>

294
00:18:22,110 --> 00:18:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fifty thousand!</font>

295
00:18:23,890 --> 00:18:25,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do we do, what do we do?!</font>

296
00:18:24,140 --> 00:18:25,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a three digit difference!</font>

297
00:18:25,930 --> 00:18:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do we do, what do we do?!</font>

298
00:18:26,460 --> 00:18:28,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}W-We train! We don't 
have any other choice!</font>

299
00:18:29,860 --> 00:18:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, just perform like you usually do.</font>

300
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:38,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a fan of the way you all 
usually perform, anyway.</font>

301
00:18:38,120 --> 00:18:39,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain!</font>

302
00:18:39,990 --> 00:18:43,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But since it's a special occasion, 
we'd love to show off!</font>

303
00:18:43,570 --> 00:18:44,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

304
00:18:44,590 --> 00:18:48,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, there's not a ton of 
spare stage time anyway.</font>

305
00:18:48,080 --> 00:18:50,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough for a CC-themed dance routine,</font>

306
00:18:50,560 --> 00:18:54,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">before coming in for a remix of our 
standard, the Marukane theme, right?</font>

307
00:18:55,430 --> 00:18:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna bring in the cheer 
team for C.C.'s agency,</font>

308
00:18:57,500 --> 00:19:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">along with the Naruhata 
neighborhood squad,</font>

309
00:19:00,390 --> 00:19:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'll need to talk to reps of 
the band and dance club later.</font>

310
00:19:04,340 --> 00:19:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

311
00:19:05,360 --> 00:19:07,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Girls, we're gonna train 
like crazy until the event.</font>

312
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:10,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No sour faces, either!</font>

313
00:19:10,350 --> 00:19:11,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

314
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone's back to normal!</font>

315
00:19:13,770 --> 00:19:15,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because we've gotta work hard.</font>

316
00:19:15,140 --> 00:19:17,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be rooting for you all.</font>

317
00:19:17,050 --> 00:19:19,510
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b><i>{\an1}<font size="20"><font color="#04090f">The next day</font></font></i></b></font>

318
00:19:18,520 --> 00:19:21,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let's start this practice!</font>

319
00:19:21,310 --> 00:19:22,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

320
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do it! Fight on!</font>

321
00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:43,160
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an7}<font color="#bfa657"><font size="25">Final Event Coming Soon!!</font></font></b></font>

322
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:51,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That just leaves the guest heroes...</font>

323
00:19:51,610 --> 00:19:55,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to assemble a who's-who 
of the Japanese scene.</font>

324
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need me for an event? Copy that!</font>

325
00:19:58,620 --> 00:20:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to show up with my team.</font>

326
00:20:01,340 --> 00:20:03,050
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b><font color="#15201d">Training</font></b></font>

327
00:20:02,180 --> 00:20:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ridiculous.</font>

328
00:20:03,360 --> 00:20:05,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not interested.</font>

329
00:20:05,510 --> 00:20:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to come! You can't 
keep me from a party!</font>

330
00:20:09,380 --> 00:20:10,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You coming, Yamada?</font>

331
00:20:10,780 --> 00:20:12,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

332
00:20:13,050 --> 00:20:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'll show up if I get the chance.</font>

333
00:20:28,900 --> 00:20:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wash!</font>

334
00:20:33,780 --> 00:20:38,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to thank you again for 
agreeing to our sudden offer.</font>

335
00:20:39,030 --> 00:20:42,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll send along a draft of the 
contract in the next few days.</font>

336
00:20:42,470 --> 00:20:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should it go to the e-mail address 
you sent me the other day?</font>

337
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right! Thank you so much.</font>

338
00:20:50,320 --> 00:20:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a pleasure to be working with you.</font>

339
00:20:57,140 --> 00:21:01,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got a pretty decent lineup, but 
it could use a little more...</font>

340
00:21:01,930 --> 00:21:06,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I should reach out to more regional 
heroes from outside the metro area?</font>

341
00:21:06,210 --> 00:21:09,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Getting All Might would be ideal, but...</font>

342
00:21:12,190 --> 00:21:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home. You seem 
to be working hard.</font>

343
00:21:14,380 --> 00:21:15,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Nao...</font>

344
00:21:15,690 --> 00:21:17,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were actually home? That's rare.</font>

345
00:21:17,940 --> 00:21:20,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just to get a change of clothes. 
I'm heading right back out.</font>

346
00:21:20,950 --> 00:21:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You always keep busy, huh?</font>

347
00:21:23,210 --> 00:21:26,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look who's talking. You even 
bring work home with you.</font>

348
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just don't overdo it.</font>

349
00:21:28,600 --> 00:21:30,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a big juncture for me!</font>

350
00:21:30,840 --> 00:21:34,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd honestly appreciate you pushing me 
more than trying to stop me right now.</font>

351
00:21:35,140 --> 00:21:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I am rooting for you.</font>

352
00:21:38,490 --> 00:21:40,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate it, Nao.</font>

353
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, can you maybe hook me up with 
your connection at All Might's agency?</font>

354
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not happening.</font>

355
00:21:47,520 --> 00:21:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a cell phone number will do!</font>

356
00:21:50,270 --> 00:21:51,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No means no!</font>

357
00:21:51,950 --> 00:21:53,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just this one time!</font>

358
00:23:26,250 --> 00:23:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Villainous hands reach out 
for the Captain's final event...</font>

359
00:23:30,020 --> 00:23:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To protect the Sky Egg from destruction,</font>

360
00:23:32,130 --> 00:23:34,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Captain engages in his most 
desperate battle yet.</font>

361
00:23:35,060 --> 00:23:36,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time: Zero Hour.</font>

362
00:23:37,050 --> 00:23:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch Japan's pro heroes assemble!</font>

